{"tid":775881,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"妻子懷孕寂寞難耐 男誘拐少年做愛","createTime":"2018-08-11T13:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T10:27:01.000Z","uid":1426,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"260cdc5480a9669b0a72b895e0abf8caef7a81d2","tid":775881,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"江蘇省連雲港市一名33歲的張姓男子，本有一個幸福的家庭，但卻在妻子懷孕後變了調。張男因不耐妻子懷孕期間的寂寞，竟透過通訊軟體認識「同性伴侶」，隨後還進一步誘拐2名13歲少年上床。<br />\n<br />\n根據《現代快報》報導，張男因寂寞難耐，沉迷於交友軟體，藉此認識不少同性的朋友，經過長時間與男同志聊天後，張男愈陷愈深，開始計畫與男同志約會。<br />\n<br />\n今年初，張男透過手機與一名13歲的少年「小王」聊天，相談甚歡後兩人約出來見面，雖張男知道小王年紀還小，只是名國中生，但還是帶他到旅館發生關係。事後，張男還叫小王介紹朋友給自己認識，隨後張男又與一名13歲小李約會，但隨即被小李的父母發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n目前張男因猥褻兒童罪被起訴，但意外的是，當地記者深入了解後，發現小王與小李並不是同性戀，只是單純好奇想要嘗鮮，才會跟大他們20歲的張男一起出遊約會開房間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NEAMNiU7RXIyvqvdFPRJuQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Mzg3O2g9NDg1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/565efd2c1579e5738621784ea99a6974\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNEAMNiU7RXIyvqvdFPRJuQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Mzg3O2g9NDg1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F565efd2c1579e5738621784ea99a6974&h=f01e8140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5acc79f7e37915502350524db0eff98ace3b8b6a","tid":775881,"uid":46170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0046eb1203fb6feb88fe569f3c661775bb505a","tid":775881,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673993d8098e7fcac773c46c258ae5e601f13a30","tid":775881,"uid":37666,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: re